name: Honey Garlic Chicken Wings

ingredients.name: chicken wings
ingredients.additionalInstruction: wing tips removed, and wings split

preparation:
1. Whisk together honey, soy sauce, pineapple juice, spices and crushed garlic.
  2. Pour honey-garlic marinade over wings in an oven proof dish.
  3. Bake at 400° F (205° C) for 20 minutes. Turn wings over and continue cooking for additional 20 minutes.
  4. After cooking, sprinkle chicken wings with 1 tbsp sesame seeds, if desired.
tips: If you do not use all the marinade, it may be stored in fridge for up to 1 month. Use in stir-fries or on Asian noodles.
